segment.source: Best practice: The computer that runs the Sequencer should have the same hardware and software configurations as the computers that will run the virtual applications.
segment.target: Best practice: The computer that runs the Sequencer should have the same hardware and software configurations as the computers that will run the virtual applications.

segment.source: The sequencing process is resource intensive, so make sure that the computer that runs the Sequencer has plenty of memory, a fast processor, and a fast hard drive.
segment.target: The sequencing process is resource intensive, so make sure that the computer that runs the Sequencer has plenty of memory, a fast processor, and a fast hard drive.

segment.source: The system requirements of locally installed applications cannot exceed those of the Sequencer.
segment.target: The system requirements of locally installed applications cannot exceed those of the Sequencer.
